    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking for a new home for my favorite ride, and I think you're going to love it! It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me over the years. I've made sure to keep up with all the maintenance, so it's ready to hit the road whenever you are. It\u2019s a comfortable, smooth drive that\u2019s perfect for daily commutes or long weekend adventures. Honestly, it\u2019s been a joy to own, and I\u2019m sure it\u2019ll be just as great for you. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and see it for yourself!",
