    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust E46 M3, a quintessential analog performer. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system that provides exceptional volumetric efficiency throughout the rev range. This example features a 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced to mitigate chassis fatigue, and the rod bearings have been addressed\u2014essential for long-term high-RPM reliability. The suspension geometry remains tight with upgraded polyurethane bushings, offering precise turn-in and minimal body roll. While the exterior displays minor honest wear consistent with enthusiast use, the drivetrain remains in excellent synchronization, delivering the visceral, high-revving experience these M-cars are known for.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
