    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 Lexus RX 350 in a sophisticated Atomic Silver finish. This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver and remains in solid condition throughout. The exterior paint retains a deep gloss, with only minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scuff on the rear passenger door that are barely noticeable. Inside, the parchment leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, and the cabin has been kept strictly smoke-free. All premium features, including the heated and ventilated seats, power moonroof, and the 12-speaker audio system, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is excellent; it has a documented service history, including a recent transmission flush and a new set of Michelin tires installed last season. It provides a quiet, smooth ride with no mechanical gremlins or warning lights. This is a turnkey luxury SUV that balances comfort and longevity perfectly.",
      "price": 34500.0,
