      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies both engineering integrity and sophisticated design. This unit has been curated to ensure a superior driving experience, featuring a robust powertrain and a refined interior cabin. It stands as a testament to disciplined ownership, offering the discerning professional a reliable and authoritative presence on the road. Inspections confirm that all primary systems operate with precision, making this an exceptional acquisition for those seeking quality and longevity.",
      "price": 34900.0,
