    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute favorite ride, and it's looking for a brand new home! This car has been so good to me\u2014it\u2019s super reliable, runs like a dream, and still looks fantastic on the road. It\u2019s been well-loved and taken care of, so it\u2019s in really solid shape for its next owner. If you're looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one! Shoot me a message if you want to come see it!",
      "price": 32500.0,
