    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and high-pressure VANOS system. The powertrain delivers a linear torque curve and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline, mated to a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a cooling system refresh. The suspension geometry remains tight, providing the precise feedback expected from this chassis. While it exhibits minor aesthetic wear consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals and drivetrain synchronization remain excellent for the discerning driver.",
